{
  "texts": [
    "It was also reported that GAI tools can provide \"outdated data\" due to access restrictions to recent scholarly work and digital databases (Abuyaman, 2023; Májovský et al., 2023; Mohammed Alyasiri et al., 2024).",
    "Other authors reported fabricated non-existent generated content by GAI tools known as \"AI Hallucinations\" which is a significant challenge in GAI development because it undermines their reliability and trustworthiness (Alkaissi & McFarlane, 2023; Carabantes et al., 2023; Firat, 2023; Mahyoob et al., 2023; Schmidt et al., 2023; Zheng et al., 2023).",
    "Another concern raised is that GAI-generated content can be biased.",
    "This issue can occur if the training data lacks diverse perspectives which can lead to biased output threatening academic inclusivity (Abuyaman, 2023; Hake et al., 2024; Mollaki, 2024; Perkins & Roe, 2023).",
    "Generated content Inaccuracies occur due to technical limitations of GAI Tools."
  ]
}